accuracyPrecisionRecall <- function(x) {
  print(x)
  print(paste('Accuracy: ', sum(diag(x))/sum(x)))
  print(paste('Recall: ', x[2,2]/(x[1,2] + x[2,2])))
  print(paste('Precision: ', x[2,2]/(x[2,1] + x[2,2])))
}

for (i in list_of_tables) {
  accuracyPrecisionRecall(i)
}
